text.tspan: Course objective
This course is designed to enable the
responsible use of public funds by providing
you with learning activities, tools,
reinforcements and testing that will help you
consistently apply your financial
responsibilities and delegation of authority
accurately and efficiently.
What’s in it for me?
This is a required course for managers who
will be responsible for signing section 32
and 34. If you don`t know what that means
yet, we promise you will understand this by
the end of the course and have the know-
how to carry out your authorities.

text.tspan: To successfully complete this course you
must pass three tests. There is a test for
each phase: plan, spend and report. To
succeed in the course you must obtain 70%
on each. You can jump to the test whenever
you are ready and retake as many times as
you need.
We recommend you use the same device
whenever you access this course so it will
take you to where you left off. If not, use the
navigation tools available on any screen to
go directly to where you need to.
